Now, I&#8217;m putting up one of my most useful Thesis 2.0 boxes for free download: PHP Code Snippets</p>\n<p><span id="more-2255"></span></p>\n<h2>What does PHP Code Snippets Box for Thesis 2.0 do?</h2>\n<p>It&#8217;s quite simple.</p>\n<p>In the same way that you can use the Thesis text/HTML boxes, you can use the PHP boxes. You simply write in your PHP code that you want to run, and save it.  See below&#8230;</p>\n<div id="attachment_2258" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="http://www.hostliketoast.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Thesis-2.0-box-php-code-snippets.png"><img class="size-medium wp-image-2258" alt="Thesis 2.0 Box: PHP Code Snippets" src="http://www.hostliketoast.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Thesis-2.0-box-php-code-snippets-300x101.png" width="300" height="101" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Thesis 2.0 Box: PHP Code Snippets</p></div>\n<p>And it&#8217;s that easy.</p>\n<p>Wherever you place this particular box with the content shown, you will get the text: &#8216;Hello World&#8217; printed.</p>\n<p>That is the power of Thesis 2.0 boxes and with PHP Code Snippets you&#8217;ll be able to place any PHP code <em>anywhere</em> within your theme. You wont need hooks, or filters, or anything like that.</p>\n<h2>How to get the Thesis 2.0 Box: PHP Code Snippets</h2>\n<p>All our free downloads are available within the <a title="Developer Channel: Sign Up" href="http://www.hostliketoast.com/developer-channel/developer-channel-signup/" target="_blank">Host Like Toast Developer Channel</a>.</p>\n<p>Simply sign-up free there and download everything you want at your leisure.</p>\n<p>You can sign-up using the form below&#8230;</p>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/hostliketoast/~4/f9ifYZ62NnI" height="1" width="1"/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:75:"http://www.hostlik